        "content": "<p>Actually I think this might work better with <code>MonoidHom</code>s instead of embeddings, but I'm having trouble defining  <code>Γ k →* Γ (k + 1)</code>. I want to be able to use <code>MulAction.toPermHom (Γ k) (Γ k)</code> but the types don't quite line up.</p>",
